com.shopgun.android.sdk.api

Class Endpoints

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.shopgun.android.sdk.api.Endpoints
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Api.Endpoint

    public class Endpoints
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains a sub-set of paths needed to request data from the ShopGun API, and has methods to generate paths, that dependent on information from objects (id's e.t.c).
